name: Warung Makan NAMASTU
address: PXJ8+RWX, Jl. Kiskinda, Kedis, Kec. Busung Biu, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81154, Indonesia
review 1: Our driver Putu took us here for lunch today on our trip from Balian to Lovina - fantastic!! Delicious nasi campur and sate lilit was soooo tasty, (enak sekali!). AMAZING view (sit upstairs, so beautiful!). Very lovely lady who served us, MATUR SUKSMA! The other review who complained about prices/their bill, which even if it was a little more, or a mistake was made, it is not a problem, the prices are local and VERY cheap for someone not from Bali - so come here, enjoy the lovely food, people and environment, and leave a positive review after your nice experience at a gorgeous local Balinese experience, it is well deserved.
review 2: Amazing place for Lunch or mini pancakes and a cool drink. Try the coffee too! Very clean and friendly with great view!
review 3: Friendly staff, clean place, perfect view and best Nasi Goreng I've ever had. The food was very good.
review 4: Cheating with prices, be careful,.check menu before you pay
review 5: Friendly people, good and affordable food.

review 3: The view is gorgeous the color for the green is really make you feel very relaxed so relaxed and I really enjoying this place
review 4: Must visit this is rice terrace view with beautiful river a long the way. Great place for rest area
review 5: The great view, mountain and the valley
